{"tid":520340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"商人治病 vs 公務員治病","createTime":"2018-01-05T10:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T12:47:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e90bb6976ebda2c3f5c73d5924a7818e79809991","tid":520340,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"香港醫療問題<br />\n<br />\n政府醫院：公務員醫病。人手短缺，但比較誠實，唔會騙你，但得過且過，傾向避免出事，逃避責任問題居多。比較不會語言藝術。<br />\n<br />\n私家醫院：商人醫病。人手充足，講求效率和利益。利益最大化。佢地可能會關心你的錢，多過你的病，而你又不知。語言藝術比較強。"},{"pid":"0b2452e012968c1fdcff61591d53e964f613e731","tid":520340,"uid":70007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"HA唔等於公務員"},{"pid":"610f2ab5960547f320350379b492a2cff4869be4","tid":520340,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b2452e012968c1fdcff61591d53e964f613e731","tid":520340,"uid":70007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"HA唔等於公務員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"Technically correct<br />\nPractically / De facto 一撚樣"}]}